PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779264378
OL,3,CYvette Cooper: Hormuz blockade risks
OL,4,Csending world sleepwalking into food
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FLast year, the UK cut its target for
OL,8,Faid spending to just 0.3% of GDP,
OL,9,Fwhile Donald Trump's administration
OL,10,Feffectively gutted the US aid agency.
OL,12,FTuesday's summit, co-hosted by the UK
OL,13,Fand South Africa, is expected to set
OL,14,Fout an approach based on "partnership"
OL,15,Fand technical advice rather than cash
OL,16,Fpayments.
OL,26,@vD@ZOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
