PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779264378
OL,3,CYvette Cooper: Hormuz blockade risks
OL,4,Csending world sleepwalking into food
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAhead of the summit, development
OL,8,Fminister Baroness Jenny Chapman said:
OL,9,F"Countries want to have more control,
OL,10,Fmove beyond aid, attract investment,
OL,11,Fstrengthen their own health and
OL,12,Feducation systems and take charge of
OL,13,Ftheir own futures.
OL,15,F"Traditional development finance alone
OL,16,Fcannot meet that call, indeed it never
OL,17,Fcould. Nor can it respond to the scale
OL,18,Fof today's challenges.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
